xtension featuring authentication and full song streaming from within the Messenger app. Read more about it on <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2017/10/5/16433770/facebook-messenger-apple-music-bot-song-streaming\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">The Verge</a>.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Personal Website V3","image":"","tech":["Jekyll","SCSS","JS","Github Pages"],"github":"https://github.com/bchiang7/bchiang7.github.io","external":"https://bchiang7.github.io/v3/","show":"true"},"html":"<p>Third iteration of my personal website built with Jekyll and hosted on Github Pages.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Interventions","image":"","tech":["Jekyll","Github Pages"],"github":"","external":"https://interventions.design/","show":"true"},"html":"<p>Interactive marketing website for Northeastern's first annual student-led design conference, Interventions.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Lonely Planet DBMS","image":"","tech":["Python","MySQL","Flask","HTML","CSS","JS"],"github":"https://github.com/bchiang7/CS3200-Project","external":"","show":"true"},"html":"<p>A simple web application that allows users to filter through and leave reviews in a database of Lonely Planet's Top 500 Travel Destinations.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"myNEU Redesign","image":"","tech":["Jekyll","HTML","SCSS","JS"],"github":"https://github.com/bchiang7/Redesign-myNEU","external":"https://bchiang7.github.io/Redesign-myNEU/","show":"true"},"html":"<p>Student web portal prototype built after conducting multiple rounds of user testing that aimed to improve the current portal to provide students at Northeastern University with a better user experience.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Crowd DJ","image":"","tech":["React","Sass","Firebase","Spotify API"],"github":"https://github.com/crowddj/crowddj-react","external":"","show":"true"},"html":"<p>Web app that allows people to crowdsource a party's music queue. Allows people to request songs, upvote songs, rate songs, etc. so the DJ can see how the crowd is feeling and queue songs accordingly. Won Best UI/UX Design at Hackbeanpot 2017.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Personal Website V2","image":"","tech":["Jekyll","SCSS","JS","Github Pages"],"github":"https://github.com/bchiang7/v2","external":"https://bchiang7.github.io/v2/","show":"true"},"html":"<p>Second iteration of my personal website. Designed and developed with a conscious effort to avoid using any superfluous frameworks like Bootstrap.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Weather Widget","image":"","tech":["JS","CSS","Node.js","Express","Heroku"],"github":"https://github.com/bchiang7/DemoWebApp","external":"http://quiet-dusk-89245.herokuapp.com/","show":"true"},"html":"<p>Simple weather app made with Node.js, Express, and Heroku. Utilized the OpenWeatherMap API and Google Maps API.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Screentime 2.0","image":"","tech":["JS","Backbone","Marionette","Cordova"],"github":"","external":"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.starry.management&hl=en_US","show":"true"},"html":"<p>Starry Station android app feature that provided users with the ability to easily filter content, pause the internet, and even create custom rules for blocking apps like Facebook and Twitter right from their phones.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"React Profile","image":"","tech":["React","JS","CSS"],"github":"https://github.com/bchiang7/react-profile","external":"https://bchiang7.github.io/react-profile/","show":"true"},"html":"<p>Online version of my 2016 resume made for fun. I was interested in learning React.js, so I found a simple tutorial and it spun into a weekend project.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"CourseSource","image":"","tech":["Angular","Node.js","Express","MongoDB"],"github":"https://github.com/bchiang7/WebDevSpring2016/tree/master/public/project","external":"","show":"true"},"html":"<p>Web application built on the MEAN (MongoDB,