ing JetBlue's HumanKinda campaign and documentary. Includes an interactive quiz to determine how \"HumanKinda\" you are. Learn more about this project <a href=\"https://us.mullenlowe.com/work/humankinda/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</p>"}}]},"extracurriculars":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Guid of International Young Physicsts Tournament","image":"","tech":[null],"github":"","external":"https://iypt.org/","show":"true"},"html":"<p>• Communicated with team Georgia to take care of their living and communication with the Tournament for 7 days</p>\n<p>• Provided technical and empirical help to teams in competition and helped the organizers to coordinate schedule and venue</p>"}}]},"contact":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Get In Touch"},"html":"<p>Although a physics and computer science major, I am also interested in photography, movies, art, traveling and fortune telling. In the processes of puesuing my interests, I get to know a lot more interesting people.</p>\n<p>So,  If you want to ask me anything or simply say Hi, I will respond!</p>"}}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":true}}}